{
  "texts": [
    "Mathematical problems assess various skills such as computation, reasoning, spatial thinking, making them inherently challenging.",
    "This often results in model performance on mathematical problems falling below expectations.",
    "Consequently, one common approach to improving models' mathematical abilities is to perform supervised fine-tune using effective mathematical instruction datasets.",
    "School Math (BELLEGroup, 2023) generates Chinese mathematical problems, including the solution process, through the model.",
    "However, the overall difficulty is low, and the answers have not undergone rigorous verification, potentially containing errors."
  ]
}